<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Kim Kardashian has added several notches to her belt since rising to fame as a socialite on her hit E! reality series Keeping Up With The Kardashians in 2009.</p>

<p>And the 39-year-old aspiring lawyer, who is currently aiming to take the bar exam in 2022, put an adult twist on her study session on Wednesday night.</p>

<p>'Tequila &amp; Torts! Was tonight's theme!' captioned Kardashian as she took celebratory tequila shots with her attorney mentors Jessica Jackson and Erin Haney.</p>

